{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qinfeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·秦風·001.1", "text_original": "有車鄰鄰，有馬白顛。未見君子，寺人之令。", "text_normalized": "有車鄰鄰，有馬白顛。未見君子，寺人之令。", "notes": "車鄰 Chinese stanza 1."}
